{"tid":390241,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"自稱關心社會的入一入黎","createTime":"2017-09-07T02:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-07T13:07:21.000Z","uid":17268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"50bc24930992f28238267c73502d42d0d8406844","tid":390241,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"政府宣傳同執行做得唔好係其一，但當大家公司 or 屋企有分類回收，唔知大家又有無做到乾淨回收<br />\n<br />\n有時會覺得好諷刺，身邊一d會關心政治社會的frd，但做呢d 野又會得過且過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n/////<br />\n<br />\n淨係搵到舊link*<br />\n<br />\n膠樽可以回收，不是垃圾，人所皆知，但香港每日卻棄置528萬個膠樽，回收率只有14%，其中一個原因是太污穢！國內自2013年實施「綠籬行動」開始，便不再回收不合乎衛生的塑膠廢料；而本地回收商又不夠人手處理塑膠廢料的清潔工序，以致膠樽落入堆填區的命運。<br />\n<br />\n原來只要大眾肯做多一步──乾淨回收，便可幫助小型回收商提升回收率。<br />\n<br />\n一步步從下而上，改變回收觀念，繼而推動政府推行生產者責任制、實施按樽制度等，讓整體回收率得以大幅提升。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/etw/%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3/article/20161027/3_55823395/%E5%85%88%E6%B4%97%E5%BE%8C%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6-%E6%94%BE%E5%85%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E7%AE%B1%E9%83%BD%E5%86%87%E7%94%A8-%E8%86%A0%E6%A8%BD%E5%A4%AA%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F-%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E7%8E%87%E5%8B%81%E4%BD%8E\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fetw%2F%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%2Farticle%2F20161027%2F3_55823395%2F%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E8%2586%25A0%25E6%25A8%25BD%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E7%25B3%259F-%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%258B%2581%25E4%25BD%258E&d=AOmWPlBs2Puzf1cKoDAMJP9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=1e197621\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fetw%2F%25E9%25A3%25B2%25E9%25A3%259F%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%25A5%25B3%2Farticle%2F20161027%2F3_55823395%2F%25E5%2585%2588%25E6%25B4%2597%25E5%25BE%258C%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6-%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%2585%25A5%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%25AE%25B1%25E9%2583%25BD%25E5%2586%2587%25E7%2594%25A8-%25E8%2586%25A0%25E6%25A8%25BD%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E7%25B3%259F-%25E5%259B%259E%25E6%2594%25B6%25E7%258E%2587%25E5%258B%2581%25E4%25BD%258E&h=9f6d1d9a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/etw/%E9%A3%B2%E9%A3%9F%E7%94%B7%E5%A5%B3/article/20161027/3_55823395/%E5%85%88%E6%B4%97%E5%BE%8C%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6-%E6%94%BE%E5%85%A5%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E7%AE%B1%E9%83%BD%E5%86%87%E7%94%A8-%E8%86%A0%E6%A8%BD%E5%A4%AA%E6%B1%A1%E7%B3%9F-%E5%9B%9E%E6%94%B6%E7%8E%87%E5%8B%81%E4%BD%8E</a>"},{"pid":"36a715251fdf732756ae0304b614bdc57d524227","tid":390241,"uid":17268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T02:41:03.000Z","msg":"平時大家會唔會洗一洗d 膠樽，清走入面d殘餘物先回收<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 睬你都on9"},{"pid":"0b7824cfb003b327cc1e96d76dcab5b3fd82f01e","tid":390241,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:36:24.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"646cc82551b30fa40b2df6a0656f0c5452ce7a61","tid":390241,"uid":143018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T04:42:47.000Z","msg":"一直都會洗咗啲樽同罐先拎去回收<br />\n就連紙都拆曬釘啊膠片啊啲不可回收部份, 再壓平/摺好少少先放落回收箱<br />\n<br />\n((由細到大屋企都係噉教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83413c32bf204468c0c423cb1ff836c49d22519b","tid":390241,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T06:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一直都會洗咗啲樽同罐先拎去回收<br />\n就連紙都拆曬釘啊膠片啊啲不可回收部份, 再壓平/摺好少少先放落回收箱<br />\n<br />\n((由細到大屋企都係噉教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n證明你屋人個教育做得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5a81b946248e86de1c5e8eb78c462bf756e333","tid":390241,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T12:36:05.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7bf2bd38222b9cd83e2ed6e5a0f79d0bf80595a5","tid":390241,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-07T13:07:21.000Z","msg":"其實都無咩用<br />\n膠樽廢紙回收商都停收（中國唔收，可以睇新聞），香港得回收業無再造業，出口唔到你放落回收箱既都係會去左堆填區（可能極小部分本地再造到，但我無data唔清楚）<br />\n下而上都幫唔到咩，無政策support上而下，民間社會幾努力都無咩用"}]}